Royal Society Numbers

Early Letters

Total letters, total sent and total received, only letters from the ‘Early Letters of the Royal Society’ catalogue.

Other EMLO Royal Society

Total letters, total sent and total received, using any letter sent where both the sender and recipient are in our list of RS members, and the letter was sent after both had been elected. Excluding any letters from the Early Letters catalogue, and duplicates.

Royal Society in the State Papers

As above, where both sender and recipient are current members (letter sent after election data of both). Two further columns listing which RS member was sending/receiving letters from that person.

SPO Letters sent between RS Members

All Letter abstracts in SPO where both sender and recipient were an RS member

RS active and inactive members

I took all RS members across both SPO and EMLO and calculated how many of their letters were to another RS member as a percentage of all their letters.
